Subject: [PATCH 12/16] feat(04-01): gate PositionConfig, BluetoothConfig,
 TelemetryConfig, and CannedMessagesConfig fields

- PositionConfig: gate Device GPS, Position Flags, Advanced Position Flags,
  and Advanced Device GPS sections (Position Packet remains editable)
- BluetoothConfig: gate Pairing Mode picker and Fixed Pin field
  (Enabled toggle remains editable)
- TelemetryConfig: gate all 3 sections (Device Options, Environment Sensor
  Options, Power Sensor Options)
- CannedMessagesConfig: gate Control Type, Inputs, and Key Mapping sections
  (Options and Messages remain editable)
- Each gated section has disabled+dimmed+footer treatment with
  "Enable Expert Mode to edit" caption2
